death of a superhero is a 2011 irish drama film based on the new zealand novel of the same name by anthony &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . originally planned to be directed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; in new zealand , the film was shot on location in ireland throughout 2010 and was directed by ian &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; . the film stars thomas sangster alongside andy serkis . it tells the story of a dying 15-year-old boy who draws comic book stories of an invincible superhero as he struggles with his mortality .